cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically with camera pose estimation in egocentric videos. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a new algorithm, which involves machine learning techniques, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with motion analysis, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and the proposed algorithm involves optimization techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
